title: HELP !!!
body: please help me my level is level 14 and apparently i moved to Oceania and the thing is in this website did not show my current level how do i move account from NA website to Oceania website ? its really disturbing to see my level is 11 but im actually 14

replies.body:
Hey JIHADZKNIGHT,

If you are still experiencing issues, this may very well be an issue with your cache/cookies on your web browser.  To that end, I strongly recommend that you clear out your cache/cookies on your web browser, by following the steps for your specific type of Web Browser in this Knowledge Base Article:

http://kb.iu.edu/data/ahic.html

I hope this helps!

Try this:

Click the PVP.net bar at the top of the screen. It'll send you to League's main page. But more importantly, it'll show what region you are signed into at the time, like this http://puu.sh/4Dgit.jpg

If you click the little drop-down arrow, it'll give you a menu to choose a region and language, like this: http://puu.sh/4DgdX.png

I don't know completely how the system works, but it might be pulling the last info it had on your account from when you were on NA (did you transfer over when you were level 11?). Changing your region on there *might* make this display correctly.

If not, it may be something funny with the beta community feature itself, and how it is reading account information.
